About This Extension

Simple extension that helps to quickly open file or project folder with TextMate with Alfred. Can be used with Alfred navigation as action. Mind that extensions works only with Alfred Powerpack.

This extension can be updated via Extension Updater for Alfred: http://jdfwarrior.tumblr.com/updater

How To Use This Extension

Use #1: textmate <input file name or path>
Example: textmate /Sites/example.com/ - open project from "/Sites/example.com/" folder
Example: textmate ~/Documents/notes.txt

Use #2: Type file or folder name and choose action "Open with Textmate"
Example: notes.txt =&gt; Open with Textmate

